nref24">[24]</a><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:7.33pt; vertical-align:super"> </span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:7.33pt; vertical-align:super"> Ralph, A.  </span><a href="http://www.thetimes.co.uk/tto/business/industries/consumer/article3771170.ece"><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:7.33pt; text-decoration:underline; vertical-align:super">Business big shot: Sir Ronnie Flanagan</span></a><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:7.33pt; text-decoration:underline; vertical-align:super"> </span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:7.33pt; vertical-align:super">The Times, </span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:7.33pt; vertical-align:super">22nd </span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:7.33pt; vertical-align:super">May</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:7.33pt; vertical-align:super"> </span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:7.33pt; vertical-align:super">2013</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:10pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:10pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:10pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:10pt">Amanda Sandford</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:10pt">Action on Smoking and Health</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:10pt">29 August 2013</span></p></body></html>